me":"2018-11-07T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以係透明，橙色，藍色？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"因為膽汁係黃色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"佢又會問點解膽汁唔可以係透明紅色藍色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ca7022cd7d7cd01eb871bd418f7d5883a9298f","tid":892952,"uid":187493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"因為你飲完咖啡"},{"pid":"ee389fc38cddb739183d66b3d2f15f1efd55fa2a","tid":892952,"uid":89694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/07/170131_ad07f631ba10f907b560aa7f3e3765bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F07%2F170131_ad07f631ba10f907b560aa7f3e3765bf.png&h=c60f6b1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e0977340d368cefdaa1633a41e4ef0bbb35217","tid":892952,"uid":2655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5684bc1e5f80a7f9f36c2fc68e8acc8bdba19d05","tid":892952,"uid":50815,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8afafaab7ae7537cc975c2652cef3c92fbf4aca8","tid":892952,"uid":171277,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"decd8bccac17e370dec36d2feff089e175264c42","tid":892952,"uid":24614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以係透明，橙色，藍色？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"因為膽汁係黃色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"佢又會問點解膽汁唔可以係透明紅色藍色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"膽汁一開始是墨綠色，所以在小腸中的食物殘渣會被染成墨綠色，但是經過腸道中的細菌分解後，膽色素會轉變成膽黃素（金黃褐色），也就是平時最常看到的顏色。 <br />\n但是在脫水（如缺水、腸道蠕動太慢）時，膽汁的顏色就會濃縮，這時就會呈現黑褐色； <br />\n反之，腸道蠕動太快時（譬如拉肚子），膽色素就來不及被細菌代謝而呈現原來的墨綠色或綠色。 <br />\n有些人吃太多西瓜，糞便會呈現淺紅色；又有些人吃了很多木瓜或胡蘿蔔，這時糞便也會呈現黃色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20061226000016KK01007&amp;guccounter=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20061226000016KK01007%26guccounter%3D1&d=vfGss2qHe%2BsvPngnLM%2FXETQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7b6fe87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20061226000016KK01007&amp;guccounter=1</a>"},{"pid":"4c58828c1c78eadfe4657815bda1ad288f55e769","tid":892952,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"便秘啲色咪黑過墨豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321a3b2a7cabbcb8b6e856f6fb5135dca375261a","tid":892952,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1e0977340d368cefdaa1633a41e4ef0bbb35217","tid":892952,"uid":2655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5684bc1e5f80a7f9f36c2fc68e8acc8bdba19d05","tid":892952,"uid":50815,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8afafaab7ae7537cc975c2652cef3c92fbf4aca8","tid":892952,"uid":171277,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"因為膽汁係黃色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"佢又會問點解膽汁唔可以係透明紅色藍色"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"膽汁一開始是墨綠色，所以在小腸中的食物殘渣會被染成墨綠色，但是經過腸道中的細菌分解後，膽色素會轉變成膽黃素（金黃褐色），也就是平時最常看到的顏色。 <br />\n但是在脫水（如缺水、腸道蠕動太慢）時，膽汁的顏色就會濃縮，這時就會呈現黑褐色； <br />\n反之，腸道蠕動太快時（譬如拉肚子），膽色素就來不及被細菌代謝而呈現原來的墨綠色或綠色。 <br />\n有些人吃太多西瓜，糞便會呈現淺紅色；又有些人吃了很多木瓜或胡蘿蔔，這時糞便也會呈現黃色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20061226000016KK01007&amp;guccounter=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20061226000016KK01007%26guccounter%3D1&d=vfGss2qHe%2BsvPngnLM%2FXETQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7b6fe87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20061226000016KK01007&amp;guccounter=1</a>"},"cited